videos.headline: Klugh to Quattlebaum with a big play for Charlotte
videos.description: Hasaan Klugh hits Mark Quattlebaum for a 23-yard pass play to get into Old Dominion territory.

videos.headline: Charlotte's LeMay rushes into Old Dominion territory
videos.description: Benny LeMay's 19 yard run puts the 49ers into Old Dominion territory.

videos.headline: Old Dominion converts on 4th Down
videos.description: Old Dominion's Jeremy Cox's runs for a 3 yard gain on a fake punt to extend the drive for the Monarchs.

videos.headline: Williams to Fulgham flips the field for ODU
videos.description: Steven Williams finds Alex Fulgham for a 19 yard gain to midfiled for Old Dominion.

videos.headline: Old Dominion's Harper takes big hit but makes the catch
videos.description: Steven Williams finds Isaiah Harper for a 16 yard gain and a first down after taking a big hit.

videos.headline: Old Dominion's defense holds on 4th down
videos.description: Brooks Barden's pass sails incomplete intended for Workpeh Kofa on 4th down for Charlotte. ODU's defense holds for victory.
